        <div class="ilst">
          <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/eagleeye/"><img src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u45205420-5.jpg" alt=" Eagleeye" class="" /></a>
        </div>
        <div class="con">
          <div class="nlst">
            <h3>
              <div class="note-toggle rr">
                <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/22095769/" class="note-unfolder">展开</a>
                <a href="javascript:void(0);" class="note-folder">收起</a>
              </div>
              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/22095769/" class="">第335页</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/eagleeye/" class=" " title=" Eagleeye"> Eagleeye</a>
                (潜龙勿用)
              
                <span class="allstar50" title="力荐"></span>
            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="22095769">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">军事思维领域集聚了人类最高的智慧。
军八股背后反映的是教条主义和形式主义。
1乘时
2勇气
3实践</span>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2012-10-30 12:00</span>
                  
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
                军事思维领域集聚了人类最高的智慧。<div style="padding-bottom:1em;"></div>军八股背后反映的是教条主义和形式主义。<div style="padding-bottom:1em;"></div>1乘时<div style="padding-bottom:1em;"></div>2勇气<div style="padding-bottom:1em;"></div>3实践
